  "body": "**Issue**\r\nWhen resizing the window manually, messages and titles do not adapt to the current window size. E.g. when I make the window smaller and then make it bigger again (manually).\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1099\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-07 a la s 1 33 53 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43789751-280f4ca6-9a47-11e8-9053-edeaf86275d5.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1097\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-07 a la s 1 33 43 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43789776-3d8c699c-9a47-11e8-8700-be5e14ef5571.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1091\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-07 a la s 12 43 34 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43789834-53ecef2c-9a47-11e8-9261-a66773b39f50.png\">\r\n\r\n**Type:** Bug.\r\n\r\n**Solution**: Elements in the UI should adapt to current window size.\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce**\r\n1- Open Status desktop\r\n2- Sign in\r\n3- Open chat with messages\r\n4- Make window smaller by dragging the corners\r\n5- Make window bigger again by dragging the corners",
